Feature: Additional features that are provided

  Scenario: Free Shipping option
    Given user is on layout8 page
    Then user scrolls to the bottom of the page
    And clicks on free shipping icon
    Then user should view page with shipping details

  Scenario: Money Guarantee option
    Given user is on layout8 page
    Then user scrolls to the bottom of the page
    And clicks on money guarantee icon
    Then user should view page with money guarantee details

  Scenario:  support option
    Given user is on layout8 page
    Then user scrolls to the bottom of the page
    And clicks on support icon
    Then user should view page with support details

